# === Life at Dogo ===
msgid "Life at Dogo"
msgstr "Dogo の日常"

msgid "A team in Fukuoka,"
msgstr "福岡のチームが、"

msgid "shipping joy worldwide."
msgstr "世界中へよろこびを届けています。"

msgid "We work hard on the craft of cross-border eCommerce — and we have a lot of fun while doing it. Here's a look behind the curtain."
msgstr "越境 EC の品質に真剣に向き合い、同時に思いきり楽しんでいます。私たちの舞台裏を、ちょっと覗いてみてください。"

msgid "Culture metrics"
msgstr "カルチャー指標"

msgid "Moments we cherish"
msgstr "大切にしている瞬間"

msgid "Nine windows into"
msgstr "私たちの仕事と遊びを覗く、"

msgid "how we work and play."
msgstr "9 つの窓。"

msgid "A growing collection of glimpses from our HQ, our warehouse and the corners in between. New photos drop every quarter."
msgstr "本社、倉庫、そしてその間にあるちょっとした風景。四半期ごとに新しい写真を追加していきます。"

msgid "Photos coming soon"
msgstr "写真は近日公開"

msgid "Team voices"
msgstr "メンバーの声"

msgid "In their own words."
msgstr "それぞれの言葉で。"

msgid "Want to be in the next photo?"
msgstr "次の集合写真に、あなたも。"

msgid "We're hiring."
msgstr "採用中です。"

msgid "Browse open roles in Fukuoka and remote — we'd love to share a Friday lunch with you."
msgstr "福岡本社・リモートの募集職種をご覧ください。金曜のランチ、ご一緒できる日を楽しみにしています。"

msgid "See open roles"
msgstr "募集職種を見る"

msgid "Send an open application"
msgstr "オープン応募を送る"

